Class SpringEdge

java.lang.Object
  es.usal.bicoverlapper.visualization.diagrams.overlapper.Edge
      es.usal.bicoverlapper.visualization.diagrams.overlapper.SpringEdge

public class SpringEdge
extends Edge

SpringEdge implements elastic edges. Elastic edges tend to a natural length and apply an (attractive or repulsive) lineal force (greater with distance to its natural length) to the nodes it connects when not in it.

Author:
Roberto Theron and Rodrigo Santamaría
